      "post_content": "@ isospeedrix\n  \n   \nNope.\n  \n   \nHeroic only triggers on a *cast*. You can get at most 1 heroic trigger per time you play a card for each creature, no matter how many times that creature is *targeted*. [Seeds of Strength](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seeds of Strength) will only give you a 5/6 on T2. Or 3 3/4s on T3 if you have 2 more favored hoplites in your hand.",
      "posted_by": "AeroSigma",
